---

<section id="reference" class="contact" aria-labelledby="reference-heading">
  <div class="contact__inner">
    <p class="contact__lede">Reference</p>
    <h2 id="reference-heading" class="contact__heading">
      <span class="contact__heading-name">Look up exact answers.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="contact__grid">
      <a class="contact__card" href="/reference/faq/">
        <p class="contact__card-eyebrow">FAQ</p>
        <h3 class="contact__card-title">Common questions</h3>
        <p class="contact__card-body">Direct answers with stable anchors for recurring integration and modeling questions.</p>
        <span class="contact__card-cta">Open FAQ →</span>
      </a>
      <a class="contact__card" href="/reference/errors/">
        <p class="contact__card-eyebrow">Errors</p>
        <h3 class="contact__card-title">Error Reference</h3>
        <p class="contact__card-body">Shared error codes, likely source, and first check for each failure.</p>
        <span class="contact__card-cta">Debug errors →</span>
      </a>
      <a class="contact__card" href="/security/threat-model/">
        <p class="contact__card-eyebrow">Security</p>
        <h3 class="contact__card-title">Threat Model</h3>
        <p class="contact__card-body">Boundaries, invariants, and the security assumptions behind Caracal.</p>
        <span class="contact__card-cta">Review security →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
